# imgproxy Security Keys
# Generate strong, random hexadecimal strings for these.
# You can use `openssl rand -hex 32` in your terminal to generate a 32-byte (64-character hex) key/salt.
# Example: IMGPROXY_KEY="c0c4e7f9a2b1d3e5f6a7b8c9d0e1f2a3b4c5d6e7f8a9b0c1d2e3f4a5b6c7d8e9"
